    • linearProjection

      public TrafficState linearProjection(double offset)
      Project aircraft state offset time, which can be positive or negative, in the direction of the ground velocity. This methods doesn't change the current aircraft, i.e., the resulting aircraft is considered as another aircraft.
      Parameters:
      offset - Offset time.
      Returns:
      Projected aircraft.
